    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-07-19T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-07-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="53" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d53">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-07-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 19,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>It is understood that a British force has occupied the island of Trinidad
                            off the coast. Representations have been made by the Government to Great
                            Britain and a war vessel dispatched to the island.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Thompson</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
